在启动画面中调用，待其完成后再展示付费墙：

```dart
try {
  final paywall = await getPaywallOrDefault(
    placementId: 'YOUR_PLACEMENT_ID',
    timeout: const Duration(seconds: 5),
  );
  // present the paywall
} on AdaptyError catch (adaptyError) {
  // handle the error or show a fallback paywall
} catch (e) {
  // handle the error
}
```
